TITLE: Checking LAPS Local Admin Password Management
DESCRIPTION: Registry check to ensure LAPS Local Admin Password Management is enabled. Verifies AdmPwdEnabled is set to 1 and exists in the AdmPwd services policy path.

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
r:HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft Services\AdmPwd -> AdmPwdEnabled -> !1;
r:HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft Services\AdmPwd -> !AdmPwdEnabled;
```

