TITLE: Checking Windows Defender Attack Surface Reduction Rules in Registry
DESCRIPTION: Verifies that Attack Surface Reduction rules in Windows Defender are enabled by checking if the ExploitGuard_ASR_Rules registry value is not set to 1 or if the key doesn't exist.

LANGUAGE: regex
CODE:
```
r:HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\Software\Policies\Microsoft\Windows Defender\Windows Defender Exploit Guard\ASR -> ExploitGuard_ASR_Rules -> !1;
r:HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\Software\Policies\Microsoft\Windows Defender\Windows Defender Exploit Guard\ASR -> !ExploitGuard_ASR_Rules;
```

