TITLE: Assigning Huffman Code Values in DEFLATE Format
DESCRIPTION: Algorithm to assign numerical values to Huffman codes based on their lengths. This process ensures codes with the same length have consecutive values and follows the DEFLATE format requirements for lexicographical ordering.

LANGUAGE: C
CODE:
```
for (n = 0;  n <= max_code; n++) {
    len = tree[n].Len;
    if (len != 0) {
        tree[n].Code = next_code[len];
        next_code[len]++;
    }
}
```

